                    "Title": "淮安 (出生地)",
                    "Detail": "<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"dc0b61983c604906b2c1c9d301d1e74f\");'><span id='dc0b61983c604906b2c1c9d301d1e74f_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1028&endYear=1029')\">1028-1029年</a>，1-2岁</div><div id='dc0b61983c604906b2c1c9d301d1e74f' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1028&endYear=1029')\">1028-1029年</a>　居乡。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"17e503a134f5478baba49078f6678380\");'><span id='17e503a134f5478baba49078f6678380_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1042&endYear=1046')\">1042-1046年</a>，15-19岁</div><div id='17e503a134f5478baba49078f6678380' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1042&endYear=1042')\">1042年</a>　自陕右归山阳，常夜读书达旦。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1043&endYear=1045')\">1043-1045年</a>　居乡。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1046&endYear=1046')\">1046年</a>　居乡。治六经，喜难注疏，有不合者，辄加点窜。尝恨康成不同时,与之对辩。诸子百家诵一遍不忘。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"01450ccff5de4b429dfc4ab7af448eab\");'><span id='01450ccff5de4b429dfc4ab7af448eab_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1048&endYear=1066')\">1048-1066年</a>，21-39岁</div><div id='01450ccff5de4b429dfc4ab7af448eab' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1048&endYear=1053')\">1048-1053年</a>　居乡。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1054&endYear=1054')\">1054年9月</a>　居乡。秋九月，有文。<span class='label'>作品：</span>书郑綮传。<span class='inlineComment2'>（活动地点为从胡瑗学还是回乡，不详。活动地点为从胡瑗学还是回乡，不详。）</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1055&endYear=1058')\">1055-1058年</a>　居乡。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1059&endYear=1059')\">1059年</a>　居乡。有文。<span class='label'>作品：</span>代慎郎中遗表。<span class='inlineComment2'>（活动地点为从胡瑗学还是回乡，不详。活动地点为从胡瑗学还是回乡，不详。）</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1060&endYear=1066')\">1060-1066年</a>　居乡。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"09a25569499a440b8a2f284de783a533\");'><span id='09a25569499a440b8a2f284de783a533_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1068&endYear=1095')\">1068-1095年</a>，41-68岁</div><div id='09a25569499a440b8a2f284de783a533' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1068&endYear=1068')\">1068年</a>　居乡。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1069&endYear=1069')\">1069年</a>　居乡。既登第，未调官而母亡。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1070&endYear=1072')\">1070-1072年</a>　居乡。庐墓服母丧。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1073&endYear=1073')\">1073年</a>　知楚州蹇公奏乞改官，迎致州序。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1074&endYear=1077')\">1074-1077年</a>　在楚州。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1078&endYear=1078')\">1078年</a>　在楚州。有诗作。<span class='label'>作品：</span>和扬掾月蚀篇。<div id='poem_501815' class='_poem'><div id='poem_title_501815' class='poemTitle showDetail'><a href='/Query.aspx?type=poem1&id=501815' class='poemCommentLink' target='_blank'>和杨掾月蚀篇</a><a href='javascript: ShowPoemAuthorProfile(26204, \"宋\", \"徐积\", \"poem_title_501815\")'><span class='poemAuthor'><span class='inlineComment1'> 宋·</span>徐积</span></a><br /><div class='titleIndent'></div></div><div id='poem_title_501815_comment'></div><div class='poemContent' id='poem_content_501815'><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_0_501815'>元丰之元岁戊午，斗柄斜指西南维。</div><div id='poem_sentence_0_501815_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_1_501815'>月行赤道日南陆，营丘分野星虚危。</div><div id='poem_sentence_1_501815_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_2_501815'>昨夕既望复今夕，盛若不损盈不亏。</div><div id='poem_sentence_2_501815_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_3_501815'>安知变起在顷刻，突如有物侵其肌。</div><div id='poem_sentence_3_501815_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_4_501815'>其始色变甚苍黄，须臾赤黑相合离。</div><div id='poem_sentence_4_501815_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_5_501815'>良久烟焰极薰燎，一团白玉烧为灰。</div><div id='poem_sentence_5_501815_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_6_501815'>黄琮苍璧不可辨，枯株死兔将安归。</div><div id='poem_sentence_6_501815_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_7_501815'>孰乌其吻吞巨皿，孰丹其汗流墨池。</div><div id='poem_sentence_7_501815_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_8_501815'>如食非食始为薄，有物无物不可知。</div><div id='poem_sentence_8_501815_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_9_501815'>虾蟆何物敢张口，麒麟何故敢争斗。</div><div id='poem_sentence_9_501815_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_10_501815'>是何星曜敢侵犯，自是其形不可久。</div><div id='poem_sentence_10_501815_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_11_501815'>君不见对月数眉毛，须臾引臂不见手。</div><div id='poem_sentence_11_501815_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_12_501815'>嗟吁天上之神物，乃有如此事。</div><div id='poem_sentence_12_501815_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_13_501815'>所蔽至甚不可解，凶而家室亡而身。</div><div id='poem_sentence_13_501815_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_14_501815'>不然借使幸而免，后世讥笑遭恶名。</div><div id='poem_sentence_14_501815_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_15_501815'>君不见汉朝贾生文有馀，其心大勇其才疏。</div><div id='poem_sentence_15_501815_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_16_501815'>当时如必用其术，纷纷不免危其躯。</div><div id='poem_sentence_16_501815_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_17_501815'>晁错堂堂蔽于刻，公孙规规蔽于谀。</div><div id='poem_sentence_17_501815_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_18_501815'>谷永之才蔽权势，有若鹰犬供指呼。</div><div id='poem_sentence_18_501815_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_19_501815'>霍光虽贤亦有蔽，何不早去显与冯子都。</div><div id='poem_sentence_19_501815_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_20_501815'>刘歆致位为国师，岂若扬雄久以为大夫。</div><div id='poem_sentence_20_501815_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_21_501815'>蔽于太高李膺辈，蔽于已甚陈蕃徒。</div><div id='poem_sentence_21_501815_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_22_501815'>窦武不断蔽可痛，柬之不忍蔽可吁。</div><div id='poem_sentence_22_501815_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_23_501815'>王允所蔽在无权，荀彧所蔽不早图。</div><div id='poem_sentence_23_501815_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_24_501815'>萧瑀<sup class='reference inlineComment2'>⑴</sup>之蔽入于佞，王衍之蔽失之虚。</div><div id='poem_sentence_24_501815_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_25_501815'>牛李虽奇蔽朋党，机云虽俊蔽附趋。</div><div id='poem_sentence_25_501815_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_26_501815'>王导蔽怨杀周顗，遂良蔽诬杀刘洎。</div><div id='poem_sentence_26_501815_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_27_501815'>崔浩蔽强杀其身，所蔽若此甚可畏。</div><div id='poem_sentence_27_501815_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_28_501815'>我爱安世真朴忠，匿名远世归至公。</div><div id='poem_sentence_28_501815_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_29_501815'>有私见求坚不许，以私求谢绝不通。</div><div id='poem_sentence_29_501815_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_30_501815'>诸葛武侯为将相，心迹皎然无所枉。</div><div id='poem_sentence_30_501815_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_31_501815'>有罪至亲而必诛，有功虽雠而必赏。</div><div id='poem_sentence_31_501815_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_32_501815'>谢安知婿王国宝，不以身蔽能辨早。</div><div id='poem_sentence_32_501815_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_33_501815'>人心自是说而服，不顾四肢与肝脑。</div><div id='poem_sentence_33_501815_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_34_501815'>苻坚之师号百万，一战而北若摧槁。</div><div id='poem_sentence_34_501815_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_35_501815'>我吟此篇不足录，却忆唐衢忠义哭。</div><div id='poem_sentence_35_501815_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_36_501815'>古人今人何择焉，大抵人心蔽多欲。</div><div id='poem_sentence_36_501815_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_37_501815'>月之所蔽惟须臾，须臾蔽去明如初。</div><div id='poem_sentence_37_501815_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_38_501815'>人之所蔽何太甚，至于终身不悟不可除。</div><div id='poem_sentence_38_501815_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_39_501815'>月乎月乎，明哉明哉。</div><div id='poem_sentence_39_501815_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_40_501815'>善去其蔽，何速之如。</div><div id='poem_sentence_40_501815_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_41_501815'>君子法之，所以改过。</div><div id='poem_sentence_41_501815_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_42_501815'>贤者法之，所以知非。</div><div id='poem_sentence_42_501815_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_43_501815'>勇决之徒，所以奋发。</div><div id='poem_sentence_43_501815_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_44_501815'>感慨之徒，所以嘘欷。</div><div id='poem_sentence_44_501815_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_45_501815'>我虽老且病，龊龊无所为。</div><div id='poem_sentence_45_501815_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_46_501815'>犹能对月吟歌诗，安得慷慨之士如桓伊，把笛为予吹。</div><div id='poem_sentence_46_501815_comment'></div></div><div class='poemNote' id='poem_note_501815'><div class='inline1'><div id='poem_sentence_24_501815_0'>⑴ 原作禹，据康熙本改，四库本作张禹</div></div></div><div id='poem_note_501815_comment'></div></div><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1079&endYear=1080')\">1079-1080年</a>　在楚州。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1081&endYear=1081')\">1081年</a>　在楚州。是年，山阳大水。有诗。<span class='label'>作品：</span>尔书长句。<span class='inlineComment2'>（《节孝集》卷二十一《玺书长句》诗序云：“元丰辛酉夏，山阳大水，太守大夫睢阳李公捍御甚力，援溺赈饥民赖其赐，全活者甚众。”）</span><div id='poem_502306' class='_poem'><div id='poem_title_502306' class='poemTitle showDetail'><a href='/Query.aspx?type=poem1&id=502306' class='poemCommentLink' target='_blank'>玺书长句</a><a href='javascript: ShowPoemAuthorProfile(26204, \"宋\", \"徐积\", \"poem_title_502306\")'><span class='poemAuthor'><span class='inlineComment1'> 宋·</span>徐积</span></a><br /><div class='titleIndent'>七言律诗</div></div><div id='poem_title_502306_comment'></div><div class='poemContent' id='poem_content_502306'><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_0_502306'>随船父老踏青莎，人各持杯奈醉何。</div><div id='poem_sentence_0_502306_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_1_502306'>谣俗恋恩成太息，吟翁乐义合长歌。</div><div id='poem_sentence_1_502306_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_2_502306'>皆知察物严而恕，谁似当官正不阿。</div><div id='poem_sentence_2_502306_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_3_502306'>东汉武威任郡守，至今高义耸峨峨。</div><div id='poem_sentence_3_502306_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_4_502306'></div><div id='poem_sentence_4_502306_comment'></div></div></div><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1082&endYear=1082')\">1082年</a>　在楚州。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1083&endYear=1083')\">1083年</a>　在楚州。有诗作。<span class='label'>作品：</span>送李守。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1084&endYear=1084')\">1084年</a>　在楚州。始受知神宗，数召对，以耳疾不赴仕。故元丰七年屡有粟帛之赐。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1085&endYear=1085')\">1085年</a>　在楚州。有诗作。<span class='label'>作品：</span>赠慎叔良。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1085&endYear=1085')\">1085年</a>　在楚州。有拘词。苏轼赴登州，过淮见先生。<span class='label'>作品：</span>神宗皇帝挽词。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1086&endYear=1086')\">1086年4月18日</a>　除扬州司户参军，特差充楚州州学教授。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1087&endYear=1088')\">1087-1088年</a>　任楚州州学教授。有诗。<span class='label'>作品：</span>谢李自明诗并序。上天章公顾子敦大河。<div id='poem_501985' class='_poem'><div id='poem_title_501985' class='poemTitle showDetail'><a href='/Query.aspx?type=poem1&id=501985' class='poemCommentLink' target='_blank'>谢李自明</a><a href='javascript: ShowPoemAuthorProfile(26204, \"宋\", \"徐积\", \"poem_title_501985\")'><span class='poemAuthor'><span class='inlineComment1'> 宋·</span>徐积</span></a><br /><div class='titleIndent'>四言诗</div></div><div id='poem_title_501985_comment'></div><div class='poemContent' id='poem_content_501985'><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_0_501985'>养以其久，真以其积。</div><div id='poem_sentence_0_501985_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_1_501985'>维积维久，是以为德。</div><div id='poem_sentence_1_501985_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_2_501985'>德而德之，或表而失。</div><div id='poem_sentence_2_501985_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_3_501985'>德而弗德，然后能造。</div><div id='poem_sentence_3_501985_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_4_501985'>孰为斯施，孰为斯报。</div><div id='poem_sentence_4_501985_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_5_501985'>德其德者，伐干以斧。</div><div id='poem_sentence_5_501985_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_6_501985'>弗德其德，培以根土。</div><div id='poem_sentence_6_501985_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_7_501985'>德乎斯乎，其孰禦乎。</div><div id='poem_sentence_7_501985_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_8_501985'></div><div id='poem_sentence_8_501985_comment'></div></div></div><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1088&endYear=1088')\">1088年</a>　任楚州州学教授。<span class='label'>作品：</span>复河说。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1089&endYear=1089')\">1089年</a>　任楚州州学教授。苏轼赴杭州，过淮见徐积。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1090&endYear=1091')\">1090-1091年</a>　任楚州州学教授。<span class='label'>作品：</span>赠庐君常。<span class='inlineComment2'>（《节孝集·赠庐君常》有“六十三翁能几年”句。）</span>题陈吏部诗后。送赵守。<div id='poem_502295' class='_poem'><div id='poem_title_502295' class='poemTitle showDetail'><a href='/Query.aspx?type=poem1&id=502295' class='poemCommentLink' target='_blank'>赠卢君常</a><a href='javascript: ShowPoemAuthorProfile(26204, \"宋\", \"徐积\", \"poem_title_502295\")'><span class='poemAuthor'><span class='inlineComment1'> 宋·</span>徐积</span></a><br /><div class='titleIndent'>七言绝句</div></div><div id='poem_title_502295_comment'></div><div class='poemContent' id='poem_content_502295'><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_0_502295'>人世情怀已索然，幸无不义入黄泉。</div><div id='poem_sentence_0_502295_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_1_502295'>不须永诀行相见，六十三翁能几年。</div><div id='poem_sentence_1_502295_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_2_502295'></div><div id='poem_sentence_2_502295_comment'></div></div></div><div id='poem_501965' class='_poem'><div id='poem_title_501965' class='poemTitle showDetail'><a href='/Query.aspx?type=poem1&id=501965' class='poemCommentLink' target='_blank'>送赵守</a><a href='javascript: ShowPoemAuthorProfile(26204, \"宋\", \"徐积\", \"poem_title_501965\")'><span class='poemAuthor'><span class='inlineComment1'> 宋·</span>徐积</span></a><br /><div class='titleIndent'>四言诗</div></div><div id='poem_title_501965_comment'></div><div class='poemContent' id='poem_content_501965'><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_0_501965'>齐有高密，有沂有沐<span class='inlineComment2'>（疑当作沭）</span>。</div><div id='poem_sentence_0_501965_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_1_501965'>旁有泰山，莒鲁郊关。</div><div id='poem_sentence_1_501965_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_2_501965'>粤有人焉，气清神耸。</div><div id='poem_sentence_2_501965_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_3_501965'>立节以高，处义而重。</div><div id='poem_sentence_3_501965_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_4_501965'>维节维义，肇自布衣。</div><div id='poem_sentence_4_501965_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_5_501965'>根本渊源，所养可知。</div><div id='poem_sentence_5_501965_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_6_501965'>以义为文，洪畅精微。</div><div id='poem_sentence_6_501965_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_7_501965'>以义持守，隐如坚城。</div><div id='poem_sentence_7_501965_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_8_501965'>以义作为，动如精兵。</div><div id='poem_sentence_8_501965_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_9_501965'>面有正色，口无谀声。</div><div id='poem_sentence_9_501965_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_10_501965'>赤心可割，肝胆可倾。</div><div id='poem_sentence_10_501965_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_11_501965'>以义接物，不矜不骄。</div><div id='poem_sentence_11_501965_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_12_501965'>以义临民，实庇汝曹。</div><div id='poem_sentence_12_501965_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_13_501965'>实康实济，实恺实悌。</div><div id='poem_sentence_13_501965_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_14_501965'>民实宜之，实受其惠。</div><div id='poem_sentence_14_501965_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_15_501965'>方今天下，虽曰治安。</div><div id='poem_sentence_15_501965_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_16_501965'>正在所恤，民有饥寒。</div><div id='poem_sentence_16_501965_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_17_501965'>公所往居，岂肯草草。</div><div id='poem_sentence_17_501965_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_18_501965'>戒吏侵渔，欲民温饱。</div><div id='poem_sentence_18_501965_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_19_501965'>言者为准，行者为表。</div><div id='poem_sentence_19_501965_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_20_501965'>维恕维平，除烦去扰。</div><div id='poem_sentence_20_501965_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_21_501965'>狼摧其牙，虎缩其爪。</div><div id='poem_sentence_21_501965_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_22_501965'>父子室家，足以相保。</div><div id='poem_sentence_22_501965_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_23_501965'>作此诗者，岂徒然乎。</div><div id='poem_sentence_23_501965_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_24_501965'>庶使其民，传告欢呼。</div><div id='poem_sentence_24_501965_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_25_501965'></div><div id='poem_sentence_25_501965_comment'></div></div></div><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1092&endYear=1092')\">1092年</a>　任楚州州学教授。知楚州蹇序辰十二月二十七日奏乞改（徐积）官；发运蒋公亦奏乞改（徐积）官。是年徐积有诗。<span class='label'>作品：</span>寄崔汝弼。<div id='poem_502291' class='_poem'><div id='poem_title_502291' class='poemTitle showDetail'><a href='/Query.aspx?type=poem1&id=502291' class='poemCommentLink' target='_blank'>寄崔汝弼<span style='margin: 0 0.5em'> 其二 </span></a><a href='javascript: ShowPoemAuthorProfile(26204, \"宋\", \"徐积\", \"poem_title_502291\")'><span class='poemAuthor'><span class='inlineComment1'> 宋·</span>徐积</span></a><br /><div class='titleIndent'>五言律诗</div></div><div id='poem_title_502291_comment'></div><div class='poemContent' id='poem_content_502291'><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_0_502291'>除却行吾义，其他任自然。</div><div id='poem_sentence_0_502291_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_1_502291'>胸中清水溜，颔下白毛鲜。</div><div id='poem_sentence_1_502291_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_2_502291'>别我未逾月，思君似隔年。</div><div id='poem_sentence_2_502291_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_3_502291'>北轩翁在此，曾醉菊花边。</div><div id='poem_sentence_3_502291_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_4_502291'></div><div id='poem_sentence_4_502291_comment'></div></div></div><div id='poem_502292' class='_poem'><div id='poem_title_502292' class='poemTitle showDetail'><a href='/Query.aspx?type=poem1&id=502292' class='poemCommentLink' target='_blank'><span style='margin: 0 0.5em'> 其三 </span></a><br /><div class='titleIndent'>五言律诗</div></div><div id='poem_title_502292_comment'></div><div class='poemContent' id='poem_content_502292'><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_0_502292'>不见吾崔子，南城两度春。</div><div id='poem_sentence_0_502292_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_1_502292'>应从湘水梦，来就泮宫人。</div><div id='poem_sentence_1_502292_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_2_502292'>壮气胸中旧，衰毛颔下新。</div><div id='poem_sentence_2_502292_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_3_502292'>明年六十六，望子过淮滨。</div><div id='poem_sentence_3_502292_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_4_502292'></div><div id='poem_sentence_4_502292_comment'></div></div></div><div id='poem_502293' class='_poem'><div id='poem_title_502293' class='poemTitle showDetail'><a href='/Query.aspx?type=poem1&id=502293' class='poemCommentLink' target='_blank'><span style='margin: 0 0.5em'> 其四 </span></a><br /><div class='titleIndent'>五言律诗</div></div><div id='poem_title_502293_comment'></div><div class='poemContent' id='poem_content_502293'><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_0_502293'>数幅长沙纸，慇勤为写怀。</div><div id='poem_sentence_0_502293_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_1_502293'>知公富情义，念我老形骸。</div><div id='poem_sentence_1_502293_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_2_502293'>处世日无几，归耕计未谐。</div><div id='poem_sentence_2_502293_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_3_502293'>若论身后事，贱骨要深埋。</div><div id='poem_sentence_3_502293_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_4_502293'></div><div id='poem_sentence_4_502293_comment'></div></div></div><div id='poem_502290' class='_poem'><div id='poem_title_502290' class='poemTitle showDetail'><a href='/Query.aspx?type=poem1&id=502290' class='poemCommentLink' target='_blank'><span style='margin: 0 0.5em'> 其一 </span></a><br /><div class='titleIndent'>七言绝句</div></div><div id='poem_title_502290_comment'></div><div class='poemContent' id='poem_content_502290'><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_0_502290'>黄艳花前白颔翁，忆君诗思入霜风。</div><div id='poem_sentence_0_502290_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_1_502290'>如今相去犹未远，明年把酒望江东。</div><div id='poem_sentence_1_502290_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_2_502290'></div><div id='poem_sentence_2_502290_comment'></div></div></div><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1092&endYear=1092')\">1092年</a>　任楚州州学教授。是年苏轼由颍州移知扬州，过淮见先生。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1093&endYear=1093')\">1093年9月3日</a>　任楚州州学教授。知江宁府曾公奏乞处徐积以太学官。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1094&endYear=1094')\">1094年1月1日</a>　任楚州州学教授。诸司公举奏乞异宠。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1095&endYear=1095')\">1095年</a>　任楚州州学教授。<br /></div>"
                },
                {
                    "Latitude": 34.587162,
                    "Longitude": 105.731276,
                    "OffsetLeft": 0,
                    "OffsetTop": 0,
