                    "Title": "开封",
                    "Detail": "<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"2daea56d18df4567848bfe3943afffec\");'><span id='2daea56d18df4567848bfe3943afffec_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1067&endYear=1067')\">1067年</a>，40岁</div><div id='2daea56d18df4567848bfe3943afffec' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1067&endYear=1067')\">1067年</a>　中许安国榜。敕同进士出身。徒步载母西入京师。不婚不仕。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"a3aace996ab04d0f861e156ca6a2e95f\");'><span id='a3aace996ab04d0f861e156ca6a2e95f_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1101&endYear=1102')\">1101-1102年</a>，74-75岁</div><div id='a3aace996ab04d0f861e156ca6a2e95f' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1101&endYear=1101')\">1101年</a>　特改宣德郎。有诗。<span class='label'>作品：</span>谢吕帅寄书诗并序。<span class='inlineComment2'>（吕帅或为吕本中。其一，百度百科“吕本中”条：“元符中，主济阴簿、秦州士曹掾，辟大名府帅司干官。”因此称吕本中为吕帅。其二，此前一年与吕本中有交往，并有《赠吕公侍讲》诗。）</span><div id='poem_501857' class='_poem'><div id='poem_title_501857' class='poemTitle showDetail'><a href='/Query.aspx?type=poem1&id=501857' class='poemCommentLink' target='_blank'>谢吕帅寄书</a><a href='javascript: ShowPoemAuthorProfile(26204, \"宋\", \"徐积\", \"poem_title_501857\")'><span class='poemAuthor'><span class='inlineComment1'> 宋·</span>徐积</span></a><br /><div class='titleIndent'></div></div><div id='poem_title_501857_comment'></div><div class='poemContent' id='poem_content_501857'><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_0_501857'>畴昔逢公时，老人悦公义。</div><div id='poem_sentence_0_501857_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_1_501857'>率然应公问，而云在藏器。</div><div id='poem_sentence_1_501857_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_2_501857'>公以问为好，其法为可传。</div><div id='poem_sentence_2_501857_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_3_501857'>老语不记时，人事成恍然。</div