                    "Detail": "<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"a591f671823949fcbcbbb3e44f6a61b7\");'><span id='a591f671823949fcbcbbb3e44f6a61b7_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1096&endYear=1100')\">1096-1100年</a>，69-73岁</div><div id='a591f671823949fcbcbbb3e44f6a61b7' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1096&endYear=1096')\">1096年</a>　特授和州防御推官。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1097&endYear=1097')\">1097年</a>　任和州防御推官。有诗。<span class='label'>作品：</span>赠袁评事。<div id='poem_502018' class='_poem'><div id='poem_title_502018' class='poemTitle showDetail'><a href='/Query.aspx?type=poem1&id=502018' class='poemCommentLink' target='_blank'>赠袁评事</a><a href='javascript: ShowPoemAuthorProfile(26204, \"宋\", \"徐积\", \"poem_title_502018\")'><span class='poemAuthor'><span class='inlineComment1'> 宋·</span>徐积</span></a><br /><div class='titleIndent'></div></div><div id='poem_title_502018_comment'></div><div class='poemContent' id='poem_content_502018'><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_0_502018'>今年七十岁，岁岁增康宁。</div><div id='poem_sentence_0_502018_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_1_502018'>人閒有寿鹤，天上有寿星。</div><div id='poem_sentence_1_502018_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_2_502018'>更若欲齐椿，但看南华经。</div><div id='poem_sentence_2_502018_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_3_502018'></div><div id='poem_sentence_3_502018_comment'></div></div></div><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1098&endYear=1099')\">1098-1099年</a>　任和州防御推官。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1100&endYear=1100')\">1100年</a>　任和州防御推官。有诗。<span class='label'>作品：</span>赠吕公侍讲。<span class='inlineComment2'>（《吕公童蒙训》：“元符三年，荥阳吕公自和州谪居起知军州。道山阳，出过市桥，桥坏堕水，而不伤焉。仲车先生年几七十矣，作《我敬》诗赠公。”按：公时年七十三，云几七十者误。《我敬》诗即指《赠吕公侍讲》：”我敬吕公，以其德齿。敬之爱之，何时巳巳。美哉吕公，文在其中。见乎外者，古人之风。维贤有德，神相其祉。何以祝公，勿乐有喜。”）</span><div id='poem_501978' class='_poem'><div id='poem_title_501978' class='poemTitle showDetail'><a href='/Query.aspx?type=poem1&id=501978' class='poemCommentLink' target='_blank'>赠吕公侍讲</a><a href='javascript: ShowPoemAuthorProfile(26204, \"宋\", \"徐积\", \"poem_title_501978\")'><span class='poemAuthor'><span class='inlineComment1'> 宋·</span>徐积</span></a><br /><div class='titleIndent'>四言诗</div></div><div id='poem_title_501978_comment'></div><div class='poemContent' id='poem_content_501978'><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_0_501978'>我敬吕公，以其德齿。</div><div id='poem_sentence_0_501978_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_1_501978'>敬之爱之，何时已已。</div><div id='poem_sentence_1_501978_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_2_501978'>美哉吕公，文在其中。</div><div id='poem_sentence_2_501978_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_3_501978'>见乎外者，古人之风。</div><div id='poem_sentence_3_501978_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_4_501978'>维贤有德，神相其祉。</div><div id='poem_sentence_4_501978_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_5_501978'>何以祝公，勿药有喜。</div><div id='poem_sentence_5_501978_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_6_501978'></div><div id='poem_sentence_6_501978_comment'></div></div></div><br /></div>"
